{
    "title": "Account",
    "category": "primary",
    "docpath": "accounts",
    "introduction": [
        "An Amatino Account is collection of related economic activity. For example, an Account might represent a bank account, income from a particular client, or entity equity. Many Accounts together compose an <a class=\"link\" href=\"\\documentation\\entities\">Entity</a>.",
        "Accounts themselves are composed of <a class=\"link\" href=\"\\documentation\\transactions\">Transactions</a>, and the sum of constituent transactions yield an <a class=\"link\" href=\"\\documentation\\accounts\\balance\">Account Balance</a>.",
        "The Accounts that compose an Entity may be viewed together as part of the <a class=\"link\" href=\"\\documentation\\tree\">Tree</a>."
    ],
    "object": {
        "name": "Account",
        "exposition": "When returning an Account to you, Amatino uses the following JSON object structure.",
        "form": {
            "root": "list",
            "components": [
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"account_id\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON Number",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "An identifier for this account, unique within an entity",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": 42,
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"name\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON String",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "A friendly name for this account",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": "\"Subscription Income\"",
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"type\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON String",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "The type of the account, one of asset, liability, income, expense, or equity.",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": "\"income\"",
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"parent_account_id\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON Number",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "Identifier for this account's parent, unique within an entity.",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": 69,
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"unit\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON String or JSON Null",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "Identifier of this account's denominating global unit, if one exists",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": "\"usd\"",
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"custom_unit\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON String or JSON Null",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "Identifier of this account's denominating custom unit, if one exists",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": "\"xrp\"",
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"counterparth_entity_id\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON String or JSON Null",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "Universally unique identifier of a counterparty entity, if one exists",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": "\"oB3cjSNKXklkJ4Tb\"",
                        "mono": true
                    }
                },
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"description\"",
                        "mono": true
                    },
                    "type": {
                        "value": "JSON String",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "description": {
                        "value": "Friendly description of this account",
                        "mono": false
                    },
                    "example": {
                        "value": "\"Revenue from sale of double-entry accounting services\"",
                        "mono": true
                    }
                }, 
                {
                    "key": {
                        "value": "\"color\"",
                        "mono": true
